# ENGRAM-INDEX.md — Lookup Index

## Purpose
Quick-reference index for targeted log retrieval. Each entry links a tag to a specific log timestamp so you can jump directly to the relevant exchange without reading the full log.

**Last Updated:** DATE_PLACEHOLDER
**Sessions Indexed:** 1

---

## How to Use This Index

Format: `[tag]: TIMESTAMP — Session N, turn T — description`

To retrieve: search ENGRAM-LOG.md for the exact timestamp.

